'''幼年特發性關節炎'''（{{lang-en|juvenile idiopathic arthritis}}，JIA）是兒童和青少年中最常見的[[關節炎|關節炎]]類型。病名中的「幼年」是指 16 歲之前發病<ref name="Merck">{{cite web | vauthors = Mehta J, Pessler F | url = https://www.msdmanuals.com/professional/pediatrics/juvenile-idiopathic-arthritis/juvenile-idiopathic-arthritis-jia | title = Juvenile Idiopathic Arthritis (JIA): Joint Disorders | work = Merck Manual Professional | access-date = 2008-12-15 | archive-date = 2015-08-02 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150802020038/http://www.msdmanuals.com/professional/pediatrics/juvenile-idiopathic-arthritis/juvenile-idiopathic-arthritis-jia | dead-url = no }}</ref>，又被譯為「兒童」；「[[特發性|特發性]]」是指沒有明確原因的疾病，即[[病因不明症|病因不明症]]，也被譯為「特異性」；「關節炎」是指關節{{tsl|en|synovium|滑膜}}的[[發炎|發炎]]。

幼年特發性關節炎是一種自體免疫，非感染，發炎性關節疾病，發病於小於 16 歲的兒童，且症狀持續超過六週以上。這類疾病通常發生在 1-6 歲的兒童中，但也可能到 15 歲才發病<ref name="Q&A About JA">{{cite web|title=Questions and Answers about Juvenile Arthritis (Juvenile Idiopathic Arthritis, Juvenile Rheumatoid Arthritis, and Other Forms of Arthritis Affecting Children)|url=http://www.niams.nih.gov/Health_Info/Juv_Arthritis/default.asp#1|publisher=National Institute of Arthritis and Musculoskeletal and Skin Diseases (NIAMS) Information Clearinghouse National Institutes of Health|access-date=19 December 2012|date=October 2012|quote=Prevalence statistics for JA vary, but according to a 2008 report from the National Arthritis Data Workgroup,1 about 294,000 children age 0 to 17 are affected with arthritis or other rheumatic conditions.|archive-date=2017-07-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170710144608/https://www.niams.nih.gov/Health_Info/Juv_Arthritis/default.asp#1|dead-url=no}}</ref>。它是兒童期可能發生的關節炎之一，可能是短暫的、會自己痊癒的或慢性的。它與常發生在成人的關節炎（[[骨關節炎|骨關節炎]]或[[類風濕性關節炎|類風濕性關節炎]]），或其它可能發生在兒童的[[慢性病|慢性]]關節炎（[[乾癬性關節炎|乾癬性關節炎]]和[[僵直性脊椎炎|僵直性脊椎炎]]）明顯不同。病因病理學上，它與類風濕關節炎相似，但較少發生顯著地軟骨侵蝕和關節不穩定，且[[類風濕因子|類風濕因子]]為陰性。

幼年特發性關節炎在歐洲和北美的盛行率約為每千位兒童一位患者<ref name="GHR2019">{{cite web |last1=Reference |first1=Genetics Home |title=Juvenile idiopathic arthritis |url=https://ghr.nlm.nih.gov/condition/juvenile-idiopathic-arthritis |website=Genetics Home Reference |accessdate=19 December 2019 |language=en |archive-date=2019-12-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191219092319/https://ghr.nlm.nih.gov/condition/juvenile-idiopathic-arthritis |dead-url=no }}</ref>。更嚴重類型的盛行率約每萬位兒童一位患者<ref>{{cite web|title=Juvenile Rheumatoid Arthritis|url=http://www.medicinenet.com/juvenile_arthritis/article.htm|publisher=MedicineNet|access-date=21 December 2012|first=William C.|last=Shiel|name-list-format=vanc|page=1|quote=Arthritis affects approximately one child in every 1,000 in a given year. Fortunately, most of these cases are mild. However, approximately one child in every 10,000 will have more severe arthritis that doesn't just go away.|archive-date=2019-12-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191205195511/https://www.medicinenet.com/juvenile_arthritis/article.htm|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

== 症狀和體徵 ==
幼年特發性關節炎的初期症狀通常沒有非特異性，包括：嗜睡、活動力減弱和食慾不振<ref name="Hoffart">{{cite journal|vauthors=Hoffart C, Sherry DD|title=Early identification of juvenile idiopathic arthritis: a better understanding helps physicians formulate treatment decisions|journal=Journal of Musculoskeletal Medicine|volume=27|issue=2|date=February 2010|pages=51|url=http://www.rheumatologynetwork.com/juvenile-arthritis/early-identification-juvenile-idiopathic-arthritis|access-date=2018-10-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181005153259/http://www.rheumatologynetwork.com/juvenile-arthritis/early-identification-juvenile-idiopathic-arthritis|archive-date=2018-10-05}}</ref>。第一個症狀，特別是幼兒，可能是{{tsl|en|limping|跛行}}。兒童可能顯得病重，持續出現{{tsl|en|flu-like symptoms|類似流感的症狀|}}。主要的臨床特徵是受影響的關節持續腫脹，常包括[[膝|膝]]、[[踝|踝]]、[[手腕|手腕]]和手腳的小關節。某些關節腫脹，在臨床上可能很難直接發現，如：脊椎、{{tsl|en|sacroiliac joint|薦腸關節}}、肩、髖和下頜等，此時影像檢查（如：[[醫學超聲檢查|醫學超聲檢查]]或[[核磁共振成像|核磁共振成像]]）就非常有用。

[[疼痛|疼痛]]是一個重要症狀。早晨[[關節僵硬|僵硬]]且之後會逐漸改善是個常見的共同特徵，這代表病因屬於[[發炎|發炎]]性[[關節痛|關節痛]]而非機械性關節痛。長期關節炎的變化包括關節攣縮（由於關節纖維化而顯得僵硬和變型）和關節破壞。各個患者特定症狀的輕重各異。症狀男女有別，且在不同地區的男女症狀也不同。推測可能受不同地區的生物學差異影響<ref>{{cite book|last1=Petty|first1=Ross E. | name-list-format = vanc |title=Pediatric Rheumatology|date=2016|publisher=Elsevier|location=Philadelphia, PA|isbn=978-0-323-24145-8|page=191}}</ref>。關節也可能發生腫脹（發炎性腫脹，或是慢性關節炎造成的{{le|滑膜|Synovial membrane}}增生和增厚與關節周圍軟組織腫脹）。

=== 關節以外 ===
眼部疾病：JIA 與前半部眼部發炎，特別是[[虹彩炎|虹膜睫狀體炎]]（iridocyclitis，慢性前葡萄膜炎的一種類型）有關，JIA 患者中約有五分之一會合併這類型的虹彩炎，且好發在女孩<ref>{{cite journal | vauthors = Weiss JE, Ilowite NT | title = Juvenile idiopathic arthritis | journal = Rheumatic Diseases Clinics of North America | volume = 33 | issue = 3 | pages = 441–70, vi | date = August 2007 | pmid = 17936173 | doi = 10.1016/j.rdc.2007.07.006 | url = http://ard.bmj.com/cgi/content/short/59/9/729 | access-date = 2020-01-18 | archive-date = 2021-08-29 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210829200322/https://ard.bmj.com/content/59/9/729 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。這類併發症通常沒有症狀，可由有經驗的驗光師或眼科醫師以[[裂隙燈|裂隙燈]]診斷。眼疾晚期裂隙燈可能發現{{le|虹膜黏連|Synechia (eye)}}。建議多數患者應規則接受裂隙燈篩檢，因為控制不佳的慢性前葡萄膜炎可能會導致眼睛的永久損傷，包括失明。

生長障礙：JIA 患者的總體生長速度可能降低，特別是疾病涉及多個關節或其它身體器官。矛盾的是，大關節（如：膝關節）發炎患者的生長可能更快，因為發炎使關節附近的骨生長板血液增加。這可能造成長短腳（兩腳長度不同），及像是[[膝外翻|膝外翻]]之類的變形。不對稱生長也會影響其他骨骼，如：手指長度不一。也可能發現骨齡（骨骼成熟度）明顯不同。

===併發症===
JIA 是一種慢性疾病，如果忽視，會造成嚴重的併發症。接受醫療專業人員適時地追蹤能大幅減少併發症風險<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.arthritis-symptom.com/Juvenile-Arthritis-Symptoms/|title=Juvenile Arthritis Symptoms|date=|access-date=2010-04-19|archive-date=2018-09-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180930201149/http://www.arthritis-symptom.com/Juvenile-Arthritis-Symptoms|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

某些類型的 JIA 常合併一種[[人眼|眼睛]]發炎的疾病，[[葡萄膜炎|葡萄膜炎]]<ref>{{cite web|title=Eye Problems and Juvenile Idiopathic Arthritis|url=http://www.aboutkidshealth.ca/En/ResourceCentres/JuvenileIdiopathicArthritis/AboutJIA/The-Effect-of-JIA-on-a-Childs-Health/Pages/Eye-Problems.aspx|work=AboutKidsHealth.ca|publisher=The Hospital for Sick Children|access-date=1 February 2012|archive-date=2017-04-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170412040938/http://www.aboutkidshealth.ca/En/ResourceCentres/JuvenileIdiopathicArthritis/AboutJIA/The-Effect-of-JIA-on-a-Childs-Health/Pages/Eye-Problems.aspx|dead-url=no}}</ref>。若眼睛發炎不及時治療會變成[[青光眼|青光眼]]、[[疤痕|疤痕]]、[[白內障|白內障]]，甚至[[視力受損|失明]]。眼睛發炎時通常沒有任何症狀或在 JIA 緩解時發生，因此對所有患病兒童來說，接受眼科醫師定期眼部檢查很重要。[[抗核抗體|抗核抗體]]陽性可預測眼睛患者的機會增加（常見於寡關節炎型 JIA）。

患有 JIA 的兒童常合併生長遲緩。此外，用於治療的皮質類固醇的潛在副作用，也可能造成生長遲緩。其他肌肉骨骼問題包括關節[[攣縮|攣縮]]、肌肉無力或萎縮和[[骨質疏鬆症|骨質疏鬆症]]<ref>{{cite web |title=Complications of Juvenile Idiopathic Arthritis |url=http://www.aboutkidshealth.ca/En/ResourceCentres/JuvenileIdiopathicArthritis/AboutJIA/The-Effect-of-JIA-on-a-Childs-Health/Pages/Complications-of-JIA.aspx |work=AboutKidsHealth.ca |access-date=1 February 2012 |archive-date=2015-05-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150525014716/http://www.aboutkidshealth.ca/En/ResourceCentres/JuvenileIdiopathicArthritis/AboutJIA/The-Effect-of-JIA-on-a-Childs-Health/Pages/Complications-of-JIA.aspx |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

延誤治療、未接受物理治療的兒童或病情嚴重的兒童，會造成手和手指的關節畸形。隨著時間流逝，手部功能尚失後且幾乎無法恢復。

== 病因 ==
JIA 的病因尚不清楚。但它與[[自體免疫|自體免疫]]有關<ref>{{Cite journal|last=Prahalad|first=Sampath|last2=Glass|first2=David N | name-list-format = vanc |date=2002 |title=Is juvenile rheumatoid arthritis/juvenile idiopathic arthritis different from rheumatoid arthritis? |journal=Arthritis Research |volume=4 |issue=Suppl 3 |pages=303–310 |doi=10.1186/ar594 |pmc=3273047}}</ref> — 代表在沒有明顯的原因下，自己體內免疫系統攻擊並破壞細胞和組織（特別是關節內）。[[生态环境|環境]]的變化刺激免疫系統，加上許多相關基因的突變<ref>{{cite journal | vauthors = Hinks A, Cobb J, Marion MC, Prahalad S, Sudman M, Bowes J, Martin P, Comeau ME, Sajuthi S, Andrews R, Brown M, Chen WM, Concannon P, Deloukas P, Edkins S, Eyre S, Gaffney PM, Guthery SL, Guthridge JM, Hunt SE, James JA, Keddache M, Moser KL, Nigrovic PA, Onengut-Gumuscu S, Onslow ML, Rosé CD, Rich SS, Steel KJ, Wakeland EK, Wallace CA, Wedderburn LR, Woo P, Bohnsack JF, Haas JP, Glass DN, Langefeld CD, Thomson W, Thompson SD | display-authors = 6 | title = Dense genotyping of immune-related disease regions identifies 14 new susceptibility loci for juvenile idiopathic arthritis | journal = Nature Genetics | volume = 45 | issue = 6 | pages = 664–9 | date = June 2013 | pmid = 23603761 | pmc = 3673707 | doi = 10.1038/ng.2614 }}</ref>和/或基因表現上的差異。實驗顯示某些突變的病毒可能誘發 JIA。幼年特發性關節炎好發於女孩，且最常出現於白種人中<ref>{{cite web|url=https://books.google.com/books?isbn=0736802797|title=Juvenile Arthritis|date=|access-date=2010-04-19|archive-date=2021-08-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210829200319/https://www.google.com/search?tbo=p&tbm=bks&q=isbn:0736802797|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

與疾病有關或可能加重病情的危險因子包括：

*基因易感性：當一個家庭成員被診斷類風濕性關節炎或另一種自體免疫疾病時，家庭其他成員或[[兄弟姐妹|兄弟姐妹]]得關節炎的機會也更高。
*性別：不論哪個年齡層，女性比男性皆更容易患病。
*心理因素：人們堅信[[心理壓力|心理壓力]]可能會加重類風濕關節炎的症狀。但是，當情緒壓力處理好後，關節症狀並不一定會消失，顯示兩者間的關係並不直接。
*免疫因素：雖然尚未找到引起關節炎的特定免疫因素，但一些專家認為誘發因子可能是像病毒感染一般，在永久破壞發生後在體內完全消失。
*內分泌：因類風濕關節炎好發於女性，推測[[性荷爾蒙|性荷爾蒙]]可能在致病或調節關節炎中發揮作用。不過，不論是性荷爾蒙缺乏或是補充既無法改善也不會加重關節炎<ref>{{cite web|url=http://emedicine.medscape.com/article/808419-overview|title=Arthritis, Rheumatoid|date=|access-date=2010-04-19|archive-date=2011-03-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110305120027/http://emedicine.medscape.com/article/808419-overview|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

幼年特發性關節炎，如同「特發性」一辭所示屬於[[病因不明症|病因不明症]]，它的病因並不清楚，且正是積極研究的領域<ref>{{cite journal | vauthors = Phelan JD, Thompson SD | title = Genomic progress in pediatric arthritis: recent work and future goals | journal = Current Opinion in Rheumatology | volume = 18 | issue = 5 | pages = 482–9 | date = September 2006 | pmid = 16896287 | doi = 10.1097/01.bor.0000240359.30303.e4 }}</ref>。目前的理解，因環境因素使具基因易感性的個體產生 JIA<ref>{{cite journal | vauthors = Førre O, Smerdel A | title = Genetic epidemiology of juvenile idiopathic arthritis | journal = Scandinavian Journal of Rheumatology | volume = 31 | issue = 3 | pages = 123–8 | year = 2002 | pmid = 12195624 | doi = 10.1080/713798345 }}</ref>。

==診斷==
由於兒童關節痛的可能病因很多，JIA 診斷困難。沒有單一檢驗可以確定診斷，且大多數醫師合併使用[[血液檢查|血液檢查]]、[[X射線|X射線]]檢查和和臨床表現以初步診斷 JIA。血液檢查測量[[自體抗體|自體抗體]]和[[類風濕因子|類風濕因子]]。然而，並非所有 JIA 患者都具有類風濕因子。此外，某些患者的血液檢查全都正常。X 光檢查的目的在排除關節疼痛的病因，不是[[骨折|骨折]]、[[癌症|癌症]]、[[感染|感染]]或是先天異常。

多數患者，會抽吸關節液並加以分析。通常透過檢驗排除關節疼痛的其他原因，輔助診斷 JIA<ref>{{cite web|url=http://arthritis.about.com/cs/jra/a/childrentoo.htm|title=Juvenile Arthritis: Arthritis Is A Children's Disease Too|date=|access-date=2010-04-19|archive-date=2010-05-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100529201650/http://arthritis.about.com/cs/jra/a/childrentoo.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== 分類 ===
JIA 主要分成三個類型：寡關節型、多關節型和全身性型<ref name="pmid18668565">{{cite journal | vauthors = Burnham JM, Shults J, Dubner SE, Sembhi H, Zemel BS, Leonard MB | title = Bone density, structure, and strength in juvenile idiopathic arthritis: importance of disease severity and muscle deficits | journal = Arthritis and Rheumatism | volume = 58 | issue = 8 | pages = 2518–27 | date = August 2008 | pmid = 18668565 | pmc = 2705769 | doi = 10.1002/art.23683 }}</ref><ref name="pmid11796405">{{cite journal | vauthors = Chen CY, Tsao CH, Ou LS, Yang MH, Kuo ML, Huang JL | title = Comparison of soluble adhesion molecules in juvenile idiopathic arthritis between the active and remission stages | journal = Annals of the Rheumatic Diseases | volume = 61 | issue = 2 | pages = 167–70 | date = February 2002 | pmid = 11796405 | pmc = 1753987 | doi = 10.1136/ard.61.2.167 }}</ref>。

